Package: nfRiskStratification
Title: Nonparametric Risk Stratification for Necrotizing Fasciitis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Sai Teja", "Bandaru", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "saitejabandaru.in@gmail.com")
  )
Description: Reproducible tools for necrotizing fasciitis clinical risk
    stratification, including descriptive summaries, partial hypothesis tests,
    nonparametric combination p-value methods, bootstrap confidence intervals,
    and patient severity ranking.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/saitejabandaru-in/nf-risk-stratification
BugReports: https://github.com/saitejabandaru-in/nf-risk-stratification/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
Depends:
    R (>= 3.6)
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
Config/roxygen2/version: 8.0.0
